{"tid":2197871,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息：立法會不續任議員可獲四年任滿酬金","createTime":"2020-09-11T02:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T06:55:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a1def9adda7c1c16dafdb755d306eba1d78f88","tid":2197871,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:48:42.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會行政管理委員會下午開特別會議，據了解，政府建議向完成四年任期的議員，先發放任滿酬金。<br />\n<br />\n根據立法會議員酬津安排，完成任期的議員可獲相等於任內所得薪酬15%的任滿酬金，即大約70萬元。<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥在人大常委會決定議員續任一年後，去信政府查詢任滿酬金的安排。消息透露，政府的回信建議，完成四年任期的議員都可獲發放任滿酬金，至未來一年會續任的議員，完成任期後，可獲另一筆任滿酬金。行管會下午開會討論有關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405152&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=371a83bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405152&h=646d807b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405152</a>"},{"pid":"eb2a776c3d61dbc04e0ae4e6ef4e5d20a8955faf","tid":2197871,"uid":133,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"Fat fat"},{"pid":"62d4035e0225733aa22d050ccf0771b84a5ef4d1","tid":2197871,"uid":166452,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:49:53.000Z","msg":"議會戰線"},{"pid":"439b5650089c043d4a1307a0de13f6d357cd5d96","tid":2197871,"uid":14494,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:51:19.000Z","msg":"等睇有人咬70萬人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0938279b6cdb0e3f0630eb8e711e75ef2251ec4f","tid":2197871,"uid":44841,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"張約四年就係四年架啦，約滿梗係要畀格，咁都仲要討論？"},{"pid":"b22ba46493c4cc17a755dee5be9ac9cdfae2e9ad","tid":2197871,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep